text: Aix-Villemaur-Pâlis is a commune in the Aube département in the north-central part of France. The municipality was created on 1 January 2016 and consists of the former communes of Aix-en-Othe (the seat), Villemaur-sur-Vanne and Pâlis.Arrêté préfectoral 15 December 2015 == References == Category:2016 establishments in France Category:Communes in Aube
title: Aix-Villemaur-Pâlis
